# Bot Battlr

## Overview
Bot Battlr is a React application that allows users to view a collection of bots, enlist them into their army, and manage their bot army. Users can also discharge bots permanently.

## Features
- View a list of bots with detailed information.
- Enlist a bot into your army.
- Release a bot from your army.
- Discharge a bot permanently.
- (Advanced) View detailed bot specs.
- (Advanced) Sort bots by health, damage, or armor.
- (Advanced) Filter bots by class.

## Setup
1. **Clone the repository:**
   ```bash
   git clone <your-repository-url>
   cd bot-battlr
